2026 Gilded Guardian - Josiah Norton
This repository contains my reflection and supporting materials for my participation in
the 2026 Gilded Guardian, a cyber defense and offensive operations exercise held in
March 2026. I competed as part of a four-person team, working to neutralize an
autonomous cruise missile swarm system by exploiting its distributed consensus protocol. 
My primary contributions were in traffic analysis, protocol reverse
engineering, and Python-based exploit development targeting the swarm's RAFT-based authentication system.
